T发行。它的发行将在五个月内标记TXT的第一场音乐，他们的最后一部音乐是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tomorrow-x-together-drop-epic-music-videow-chasing-that-feeling-3514534">他们的第三张录音室专辑“ The Name Chapty：FreeFall”</a> 。</p><p>该唱片是由单一的“追逐这种感觉”领导的，并将合作包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/txt-anitta-back-for-more-tomorrow-x-together-3493268">“更多”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/txt-jonas-brother-do-it-like-that-3459307">“这样做”</a> ，分别以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anitta">Anitta</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-jonas-brothers">Jonas Brothers</a>为特色。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/txt-taehyun-cover-bruno-mars-finesse-3602565">观看TXT的Taehyun封面Bruno Mars的“ Finesse”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
